00:35:43,700 --> 00:35:44,980
Just focus ahead,

540
00:35:46,780 --> 00:35:48,240
Be steady for every step.

541
00:35:49,320 --> 00:35:50,740
The finish line will come.

542
00:35:51,240 --> 00:35:52,780
Go for it, Jiang Qiaoxi!

543
00:35:53,640 --> 00:35:55,720
No need to rush. Just focus ahead,

544
00:35:56,220 --> 00:35:57,940
Be steady for every step.

545
00:35:57,980 --> 00:36:00,180
The finish line will come.

546
00:36:00,960 --> 00:36:02,120
That's exactly

547
00:36:02,660 --> 00:36:04,440
what I told you

548
00:36:05,060 --> 00:36:06,160
at the fourth-grade field day.

549
00:36:06,660 --> 00:36:07,720
That's right.

550
00:36:08,940 --> 00:36:10,400
Now it's my turn to say it to you.

551
00:36:10,440 --> 00:36:11,620
<i>Go for it, Yu Qiao!</i>

552
00:36:11,660 --> 00:36:12,760
Don't think by doing it,

553
00:36:12,800 --> 00:36:14,340
<i>- Go for it, Yu Qiao!</i>
<i>- Keep up!</i>

554
00:36:14,380 --> 00:36:16,280
I'll get you that half letter.

555
00:36:17,040 --> 00:36:17,880
No rush.

556
00:36:18,620 --> 00:36:19,960
- You can do it later.
<i>- Come on!</i>

557
00:36:20,000 --> 00:36:21,260
<i>Yu Qiao!</i>

558
00:36:21,760 --> 00:36:22,600
<i>Hang on!</i>

559
00:36:23,100 --> 00:36:24,580
<i>Go for it!</i>

560
00:36:25,520 --> 00:36:26,920
- Keep it up!
- Keep up!

561
00:36:26,960 --> 00:36:28,400
- Yu Qiao, Go for it!
- Go for it!

562
00:36:29,740 --> 00:36:30,680
<i>Go for it!</i>

563
00:36:31,180 --> 00:36:32,460
<i>Take it slow.</i>

564
00:36:32,960 --> 00:36:33,800
<i>Hang on!</i>

565
00:36:33,840 --> 00:36:35,100
<i>- Hang on, Yu Qiao!</i>
<i>- Yu Qiao!</i>

566
00:36:35,960 --> 00:36:36,800
Tenth to the line.

567
00:36:42,440 --> 00:36:43,680
- Are you okay?
- Are you okay?

568
00:36:43,720 --> 00:36:45,260
- Okay?
- Be careful.

569
00:36:45,300 --> 00:36:46,640
- Go to the infirmary.
- Go.

570
00:36:46,680 --> 00:36:47,540
<i>Under this blue sky,</i>

571
00:36:47,580 --> 00:36:48,480
<i>- Their friendship shines.</i>
- Be careful.

572
00:36:48,520 --> 00:36:50,640
- Take it easy.
<i>- On this arduous journey,</i>

573
00:36:50,680 --> 00:36:52,140
- <i>they stood for each other,</i>
- Careful.

574
00:36:52,180 --> 00:36:53,740
<i>with deepest sincerity.</i>

575
00:36:53,780 --> 00:36:57,180
<i>In this very moment,</i>
<i>their friendship transcends into legend.</i>

576
00:36:57,220 --> 00:36:58,680
<i>- Thank you, Ms.</i>
<i>- Be careful.</i>

577
00:36:59,820 --> 00:37:00,860
- Alright?
- Alright.

578
00:37:00,900 --> 00:37:02,140
Well? You're not lame, are you?

579
00:37:02,640 --> 00:37:04,260
- Slow down.
- Qin Yeyun.

580
00:37:04,760 --> 00:37:06,240
Could you find a nicer way to say that?

581
00:37:06,780 --> 00:37:08,200
So, are you alright?

582
00:37:08,740 --> 00:37:09,940
Alright.

583
00:37:09,980 --> 00:37:11,560
Just a sprained ankle.

584
00:37:11,600 --> 00:37:13,220
Some spray and rest,
good as new in two days.

585
00:37:15,200 --> 00:37:16,200
Where is Jiang Qiaoxi?

586
00:37:16,760 --> 00:37:17,940
He went back to study,

587
00:37:17,980 --> 00:37:19,680
got that winter camp coming up.

588
00:37:20,520 --> 00:37:23,120
But he only left
after making sure you were okay.

589
00:37:23,740 --> 00:37:25,480
He shouldn't have come today at all.

590
00:37:26,140 --> 00:37:27,900
With the Olympiad this close,

591
00:37:28,460 --> 00:37:29,520
and that head injury?

592
00:37:29,560 --> 00:37:32,180
He should stay home study
and take some more rest.

593
00:37:32,220 --> 00:37:33,520
Why is he here?

594
00:37:33,560 --> 00:37:34,620
To enjoy the show

595
00:37:34,660 --> 00:37:36,180
that you clinched last place.

596
00:37:37,500 --> 00:37:40,000
Running around with a busted head.

597
00:37:40,500 --> 00:37:41,720
He is not kids anymore.

598
00:37:42,220 --> 00:37:44,020
When will he learn to
take care of himself?

599
00:37:46,700 --> 00:37:48,380
Are you concerned about Jiang Qiaoxi?

600
00:37:49,560 --> 00:37:50,440
Don't be ridiculous.

601
00:37:50,480 --> 00:37:51,800
Impossible.

602
00:37:52,520 --> 00:37:54,140
Why on earth would I care about him?

603
00:38:00,380 --> 00:38:01,380
Jiang Qiaoxi.

604
00:38:05,320 --> 00:38:06,300
Jiang Qiaoxi.

605
00:38:08,120 --> 00:38:10,540
How is your wound?
Are you feeling better now?

606
00:38:11,040 --> 00:38:12,500
Didn't my mom tell you?

607
00:38:14,900 --> 00:38:16,340
I'm just very worried about you.

608
00:38:16,380 --> 00:38:17,620
We are friends.

609
00:38:19,520 --> 00:38:21,460
You don't even understand
the meaning of friendship.

610
00:38:23,440 --> 00:38:25,860
Real friends push each other forward.

611
00:38:25,900 --> 00:38:27,380
They make you better,

612
00:38:27,880 --> 00:38:29,080
never harm you,

613
00:38:29,120 --> 00:38:31,400
and certainly don't come
between your family.

614
00:38:32,200 --> 00:38:34,240
My friend didn't hurt me.

615
00:38:34,280 --> 00:38:36,380
I am happy that I can do that for her.

616
00:38:37,660 --> 00:38:38,640
And honestly,

617
00:38:39,320 --> 00:38:42,840
I'm doing much better now.

618
00:38:46,600 --> 00:38:48,740
Feel free to report
all this back to my mom.

619
00:38:49,880 --> 00:38:51,040
Jiang Qiaoxi.

620
00:38:51,540 --> 00:38:53,360
Stop being so stubborn and wake up!

621
00:39:02,420 --> 00:39:03,500
How is Yu Qiao's foot?

622
00:39:04,760 --> 00:39:07,800
He said it was just a mild sprain,
nothing serious.

623
00:39:11,740 --> 00:39:13,720
He used to top
in the long-distance race every year.

624
00:39:13,760 --> 00:39:15,380
But he came in last this year.

625
00:39:15,420 --> 00:39:16,860
I hope he's not too upset.

626
00:39:16,900 --> 00:39:19,660
How did you know
he won first place every year?

627
00:39:19,700 --> 00:39:21,100
Of course I know!

628
00:39:22,360 --> 00:39:23,760
I also know

629
00:39:23,800 --> 00:39:26,480
Yu Qiao dreams of
becoming an air force pilot.

630
00:39:26,520 --> 00:39:28,540
That's why he cares particularly
about his eyesight.

631
00:39:29,540 --> 00:39:30,760
As for Du Shang,

632
00:39:31,260 --> 00:39:32,900
he wants to study medicine,

633
00:39:33,420 --> 00:39:36,680
so he spends all his free time
reading medical books.

634
00:39:37,380 --> 00:39:38,700
And Cai Fangyuan,

635
00:39:38,740 --> 00:39:42,400
he's been working on his own
literature website since Year 10.

636
00:39:44,220 --> 00:39:46,420
So you've been secretly
keeping an eye on them all along.

637
00:39:46,460 --> 00:39:47,420
Of course.

638
00:39:50,140 --> 00:39:51,100
But

639
00:39:52,280 --> 00:39:55,380
all I can do is watch them from afar.

640
00:39:57,160 --> 00:39:59,000
You deserve real praise
for staying with Yu Qiao

641
00:39:59,040 --> 00:40:00,780
all the way to the finish line today.

642
00:40:00,820 --> 00:40:01,660
Tada!

643
00:40:02,380 --> 00:40:03,740
There's nothing to praise.

644
00:40:04,240 --> 00:40:05,340
This is just who I am.

645
00:40:06,100 --> 00:40:08,400
I just never got the chance
to show it before.

646
00:40:13,220 --> 00:40:14,940
Well you'll have to work hard for it.

647
00:40:15,640 --> 00:40:17,900
Cai Fangyuan and Du Shang's hearts

648
00:40:17,940 --> 00:40:19,520
are still ice-cold towards you.

649
00:40:20,020 --> 00:40:22,520
Whether they'll accept you back
in Qunshan Squard,

650
00:40:23,580 --> 00:40:24,720
it is still a question.

651
00:40:27,740 --> 00:40:28,600
Really?

652
00:40:29,100 --> 00:40:30,400
Really.

653
00:40:30,440 --> 00:40:31,820
I tried to persuade them but fail.

654
00:40:41,360 --> 00:40:43,240
Relax, Yingtao.

655
00:40:43,280 --> 00:40:45,500
I'll make sure they come around.

656
00:40:46,040 --> 00:40:47,120
And worst case,

657
00:40:47,160 --> 00:40:48,460
you've got my back, right?

658
00:40:48,500 --> 00:40:50,500
Ms. Lin, teach me, please.

659
00:40:50,540 --> 00:40:52,480
You're the expert at fixing things.

660
00:40:54,440 --> 00:40:55,800
Those two.

661
00:40:56,300 --> 00:40:58,120
They've invited you
to the beach this Saturday.

662
00:40:58,660 --> 00:41:01,240
Whether you can win them over
and melt their icy hearts,

663
00:41:01,280 --> 00:41:03,100
well, that's up to you now.

664
00:41:04,080 --> 00:41:05,220
You've only got one shot.

665
00:41:07,440 --> 00:41:09,900
The beach?

666
00:41:24,680 --> 00:41:25,520
Okay.

667
00:41:26,020 --> 00:41:28,540
I'll work hard.

668
00:41:28,580 --> 00:41:30,020
I'll prove myself.

669
00:41:35,020 --> 00:41:35,940
What's so funny?

670
00:41:38,540 --> 00:41:40,200
Oh come on, why so serious?

671
00:41:41,100 --> 00:41:43,340
- Come on.
- You're kidding me?

672
00:41:45,900 --> 00:41:47,620
Did you see your face just now?

673
00:41:48,560 --> 00:41:50,800
They were totally messing with me.

674
00:41:50,840 --> 00:41:51,960
But who do they think I am?

675
00:41:52,000 --> 00:41:53,140
I'm way too clever

676
00:41:53,180 --> 00:41:54,780
to fall for that.

677
00:41:56,120 --> 00:41:58,180
That beach invitation?
It's obviously their way

678
00:41:58,220 --> 00:42:01,740
to officially welcome you back
to the Qunshan Squard.

679
00:42:02,980 --> 00:42:04,300
So it's a welcome.

680
00:42:04,880 --> 00:42:07,240
And here I was,
all geared up to face their trials.

681
00:42:08,820 --> 00:42:10,620
I've made up my mind. This Saturday,

682
00:42:10,660 --> 00:42:12,960
we're going to the beach
to set off fireworks.

683
00:42:14,400 --> 00:42:17,100
We'll make up for the ones
we missed last time.

684
00:42:57,960 --> 00:42:58,800
My goodness.

685
00:42:58,840 --> 00:42:59,680
How beautiful!

686
00:42:59,720 --> 00:43:01,440
Look at this one. Looks like a butterfly.

687
00:43:01,480 --> 00:43:02,560
- Look!
- Wow.

688
00:43:09,540 --> 00:43:11,600
Lin Yingtao, what's wrong with you?

689
00:43:12,660 --> 00:43:14,080
Isn't it beautiful?

690
00:43:15,100 --> 00:43:16,080
It's good.

691
00:43:16,580 --> 00:43:17,640
Very beautiful.

692
00:43:19,120 --> 00:43:21,160
Why is it so beautiful?

693
00:43:22,140 --> 00:43:24,120
It's annoying.

694
00:43:25,380 --> 00:43:27,140
Why is it annoying?

695
00:43:28,460 --> 00:43:29,500
Because…

696
00:43:32,520 --> 00:43:34,220
Jiang Qiaoxi's not here.

697
00:43:34,260 --> 00:43:35,940
Don't cry, Ling Yingtao.

698
00:43:35,980 --> 00:43:37,360
No crying during New Year's.

699
00:43:42,940 --> 00:43:44,140
Seven years.

700
00:43:44,780 --> 00:43:46,140
Seven long years.

701
00:43:46,640 --> 00:43:48,060
They are all behind us now.

702
00:43:50,660 --> 00:43:51,520
Jiang Qiaoxi.

703
00:43:52,020 --> 00:43:55,380
We've got so many more
seven-year chapters ahead of us.

704
00:43:57,140 --> 00:43:57,980
True.

705
00:43:58,480 --> 00:43:59,460
For the future,

706
00:43:59,960 --> 00:44:02,060
we have many more
seven-year chapters to come.

